{"type": "article", "id": 28087, "title": "模块型家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-13T07:00:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021340282s9mXoYfZFCNeM1I.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>想要让椅子坐得舒服，不如就自己动手拼一把吧。以人类脊柱为灵感，立陶宛设计师 Mindaugas Zillions 设计了一款名为 Spyndi 的模块型家具。它由 60 根木条连接而成，坚固而灵活。每一根木条分为 A、B 两端，同一端相连后就能组成曲线，不同端相连后则可以形成直线，根据需要进行组合搭配就能创造出任意形状的家具。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/spyndi/amazing-furniture-invention-magic-sticks\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 1850 欧元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134025BNVC1e5AQ8YGcHUE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134025uYF0RypQ7UIctVLx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134026mZAINr2kuFRfWv1a.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73529412\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134027ofq91OBmCUzZHJMv.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}